# Never commit raw asset archives (extract them instead)
public/assets/**/*.zip
# Raw extracted asset packs (~169MB, mostly unused source/.aseprite/sample files). They stay on
# disk for the renderer-integration work; only the specific curated sprites the renderer loads get
# committed (force-add them under public/assets/curated/). The manifest IS tracked (see below).
public/assets/*/
!public/assets/curated/
game.db
game.db-shm
game.db-wal
.shots/
